item.title: CVE-2021-24857|2024-08-03T19:42:17.347Z -- unknown -- totop%20link
item.description: The ToTop Link WordPress plugin through 1.7.1 passes base64 encoded user input to the unserialize() PHP function, which could lead to PHP Object injection if a plugin installed on the blog has a suitable gadget chain.
